You can call any of the revision management API functions in your view code:

https://django-reversion.readthedocs.io/en/stable/api.html#revision-api

For example:

``` py
import reversion

class YourView(RevisionMixin, YourBaseView):

    def post(self, request):
        reversion.set_comment("foo bar")
        return super().post(request)
```

